Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA09C6&\bord0\fs35\pos(441,427)}蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA09C6&\bord0\fs35\pos(851,427)}青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA09C6&\bord0\fs35\pos(1125,427)}其他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「姬誉蛙」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「每16年在陆地上出现一次的 奇迹般的青蛙」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「把这个青蛙放在16岁女生的脸上 让它发汗」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「收集18毫升汗水 给喜欢的男人喝下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「哎呀 真不可思议」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「他马上就会成为你的俘虏」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「他一定会向你做出爱的告白吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「哎呀 真不可思议」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「他马上就会成为你的俘虏」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行 绝对不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然说想要和我谈谈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 今晚百合小姐怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正忙着排练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要结束巡演了 每天都干劲十足练到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请喝点咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是用特别的水冲泡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让你热起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确有股不可思议的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉是有点野生味…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多…蕗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呱…呱呱呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多…多蕗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 苹果!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 这心情已然无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 我是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你拐走而来!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把我拐走吧! 王子殿下!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何至今未曾留意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我这一候鸟合翅休憩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就只有你明眸深处的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一汪爱之泉水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快看 苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBBFF96&\3c&H6CB842&\shad0\be3\bord3\fs40\move(480,377,490,377,0,413)}桂树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8FA5FE&\3c&H4351B9&\be3\shad0\bord3\fs40\move(480,459,490,459,0,413)}苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会变得幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBBFF96&\3c&H6CB842&\shad0\be3\bord3\fs50\frx4\fry332\fay-0.1\frz4.097\pos(207,237)}桂树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\be3\bord3\fs50\frx-4\fry-332\fay0.2\c&H92B8F2&\3c&H656EE0&\frz359.852\pos(1052,223)}苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像日记上写的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:12.03,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(734,432)}忠犬八公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H606066&\shad2\bord0\4c&H333339&\pos(750,398)}桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H606066&\shad2\bord0\4c&H333339&\pos(750,463)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H606066&\shad2\bord0\4c&H333339&\pos(750,521)}苹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出生之前 我们的命运早已紧紧相连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今发生的事只是一小场爱情歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱的考验罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的丘比特之箭可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射往此处的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,660)}Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中红心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 Je t'aime, mon amour
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}法语「我爱你，我的爱人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往爱的城堡吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人会永远高歌下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要合二为一了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败也好 失望也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果都是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这一切一定都是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一滴眼泪都不会是白流的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这一刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与桃果合为一体的这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那么地期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就坦率地面对这份感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅子 要溢出来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这是怎么了 恍恍惚惚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶 你跟苹果之间发生了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶做卷心菜卷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多都是想跟别人和好的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止的吵架对象 都只是小冠一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望苹果也能喜欢卷心菜卷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和荻野目…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那种关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是你妹妹非常重要的女性朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要重归于好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妹妹的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还是做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是如此地相爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着多蕗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该是命中注定的恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…蕗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱 呱呱呱呱呱呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果! 快把门打开啊 呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 别怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 欢迎你来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百…百合小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果 快开门呱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.79,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}呐 苹果~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请与多蕗…分手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}苹果 就让我做你的小鸟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我爱你啊苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你也听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗他现在 已经不会爱上除我以外的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 把多蕗让给我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.15,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}苹果 快把我放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}让我们乘上爱的滑翔伞一同飞翔吧 Let's 呱 go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你说话啊 苹果!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样 你就能得到幸福了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当然会幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟多蕗结婚 建个小家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小狗跟小孩 全家幸福地在一起!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为 苹果你肯定是喜欢高仓晶马的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜欢他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢他…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没注意到自己真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对晶马…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:17:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才是喜欢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 泡点fabulous的茶来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果! 快开门呱!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是无法停息的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.40,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(998,253)}然而 因为其效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.40,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1126,253)}只限一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.15,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1126,253)}只限一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:05.90,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1126,253)}只限一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.40,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1126,253)}只限一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.40,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1044,291)}所以只能作为最终手段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果 欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来得好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想你会不会饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和阳毬做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵! 高仓家特制! 咖喱味卷心菜卷!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为荻野目你很喜欢咖喱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能做得有些多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才讨厌你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…不都是你的错嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要打我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是喜欢多蕗的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱多蕗的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要和他结合在一起成为桃果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是命运! 是我出生的理由!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让家人团圆的杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不都被你给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连鞋也不脱就冒冒失失地冲进我的命运里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今为止的努力全部都泡汤了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要出现在我的面前?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要说「我就是我」啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么! 为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是我的什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存战略!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine——!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知你等必将一事无成之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭吧 母猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候我就特别允许你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放开喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把肚子里的苦水都倾吐一空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道我家的「咖喱日」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻野目桃果每月的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家都会一起吃她最喜欢的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就在同一天 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「16年前」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是那个「莫非」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐 荻野目桃果 是那个事件的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在姐姐死的同时出生的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是桃果的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和多蕗在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没出现在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会进行得很顺利!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平时那样说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 16年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搅乱你命运的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说蠢话!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起16年前 你还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和老哥冠叶出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们 你的姐姐才会去世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在…说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 你姐姐的去世…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来进行生存战略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:54.84,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}11{\fs30\pos(640,630)}TH STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:54.84,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:16.22,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}全てがもし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.89,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}決められてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:28.91,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らはどうして　もがくのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:33.07,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}それは、君じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:36.77,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}君の、せいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:44.26,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲しみはもうたくさんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:48.11,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}だから、そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.04,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今の、ままじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:59.71,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}うまく伝えきれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:07.12,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:16.06,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:16.22,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如果这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.89,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:28.91,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我们又为何 仍在苦苦挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:33.07,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}其实那 与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:36.77,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你并没有 做错什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:44.26,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲伤已经足够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:48.11,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}因此 并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.04,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}并不是 现在这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:59.71,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}只是无法将心情传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:07.12,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:16.06,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 全部都是我们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搅乱你命运的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存战略 妹妹的命令